getUi5VersionParameters.description: Returns the URL parameters needed for running an application with a specific UI5 version.

params.name: sUi5Version
params.description: selected UI5 version from the run configurations, for example "1.40.9"

returns.description: Array of the URL parameters for for running an application with a specific UI5 version. For example [{"name":"hc_appversion.sapui5preview", "value":"1.40.9"}]
